					<paragraph lineSpacing="1_1_2"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[19.  Your services shall be terminable by either party giving the other 1 (One) month notice. Company may, however, reduce this notice period at its discretion by accepting / paying basic salary in lieu the thereof. Your resignation will not be deemed or accepted till it is accepted/confirmed in writing by an authorized signatory from HR Department of the Company.]]></text>
			</staticText>
