					<paragraph lineSpacing="1_1_2"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[20. If you are found guilty of any misconduct or should you commit any breach of the service conditions or get involved in an act, which in the opinion of the company is prejudicial to the interest of the company, the company may without any previous notice or termination payment, terminate your services.]]></text>
			</staticText>
